 &#273;i&#7873;u kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; b&#7887; qua l&agrave; x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng cho m&igrave;nh m&#7897;t h&#7879; th&#7889;ng offpage th&#7853;t s&#7921; v&#7919;ng m&#7841;nh. C&oacute; r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u th&#7911; thu&#7853;t &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y khi &#273;&#7871;n v&#7899;i Youtubestore.vn. N&#417;i c&oacute; th&#7875; gi&uacute;p b&#7841;n &#273;&#7841;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7919;ng k&#7923; v&#7885;ng v&#7899;i kinh nghi&#7879;m nhi&#7873;u n&#259;m trong l&#297;nh v&#7921;c n&agrave;y.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.7999999999999998;text-align: justify;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Ngo&agrave;i ra, c&ograve;n nhi&#7873;u &#273;i&#7873;u c&#7847;n bi&#7871;t khi mua b&aacute;n nh&#432;&#7907;ng quy&#7873;n&nbsp; k&ecirc;nh youtube uy t&iacute;n t&#7841;i VN t&#7841;i Youtubestore.vn. Ch&#7855;c h&#7859;n v&#7899;i s&#7921; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; th&ocirc;ng minh t&#7841;i n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng n&agrave;y, b&#7841;n s&#7869; cho m&igrave;nh s&#7921; l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n &#273;&uacute;ng &#273;&#7855;n trong vi&#7879;c x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng t&#7915; &#273;&acirc;u v&agrave; n&ecirc;n b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u nh&#432; th&#7871; n&agrave;o? V&#7899;i s&#7921; h&#7895; tr&#7907; t&#7889;t nh&#7845;t t&#7915; nh&#7919;ng k&ecirc;nh &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7841;o v&agrave; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n tr&ecirc;n Youtube, ch&#7855;c ch&#7855;n s&#7869; &#273;em l&#7841;i cho b&#7841;n nh&#7919;ng l&#7907;i th&#7871; h&#417;n r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u l&#7847;n.</span></p><p></p></p>\n', 1, '2021-05-05 15:04:10', '2021-05-06 21:25:59');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `language`, `name`, `image`, `slug`, `content`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(109, 'vi', 'Cách tạo kênh youtube mới nhất 2021', '/images/upload/post/109/cach-tao-kenh-youtube-lnv.jpg', 'cach-tao-kenh-youtube-moi-nhat-2021', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.7999999999999998;text-align: justify;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:2pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">B&#7841;n &#273;ang mu&#7889;n t&#7841;o k&ecirc;nh Youtube cho m&igrave;nh nh&#432;ng ch&#432;a bi&#7871;t b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#7915; &#273;&acirc;u? Youtubestore.vn s&#7869; h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n b&#7841;n c&aacute;ch t&#7841;o k&ecirc;nh Youtube m&#7899;i nh&#7845;t t&#7915; A-Z ngay trong 3 ph&uacute;t &#273;&#7885;c. &#272;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i, c&#361;ng s&#7869; h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n cho b&#7841;n c&aacute;ch c&aacute;ch c&agrave;i &#273;&#7863;t c&aacute;c t&ugrave;y ch&#7881;nh &#273;&#7875; k&ecirc;nh tr&ocirc;ng b&#7855;t m&#7855;t v&agrave; chuy&ecirc;n nghi&#7879;p h&#417;n ngay trong b&agrave;i vi&#7871;t n&agrave;y. C&ugrave;ng theo d&otilde;i nh&eacute;.</span><h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.7999999999999998;text-align: justify;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:2pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">1. T&#7841;o k&ecirc;nh Youtube &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m g&igrave;?</span></h2><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.7999999999999998;text-align: justify;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:2pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Youtube hi&#7879;n l&agrave; m&#7897;t n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng chia s&#7867; video l&#7899;n nh&#7845;t to&agrave;n c&#7847;u, tr&ecirc;n &#273;&oacute; ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; chia s&#7867; nh&#7919;ng video m&agrave; m&igrave;nh s&aacute;ng t&#7841;o ra v&agrave; m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i tr&ecirc;n th&#7871; gi&#7899;i c&oacute; th&#7875; xem &#273;&#432;&#7907;c n&#7897;i dung c&#7911;a video n&agrave;y ch&#7881; th&ocirc;ng qua 1 c&uacute; click chu&#7897;t. Ngo&agrave;i ra, khi c&oacute; t&agrave;i kho&#7843;n Youtube ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; tho&#7843;i m&aacute;i comment, like, dislike &#273;&#7875; th&#7875; hi&#7879;n c&#7843;m c&#7843;m x&uacute;c v&agrave; nh&#7919;ng quan &#273;i&#7875;m c&aacute; nh&acirc;n.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.7999999999999998;text-align: justify;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:2pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">&#272;&#7875; c&oacute; th&#7875; upload &#273;&#432;&#7907;c video l&ecirc;n Youtube b&#7855;t bu&#7897;c ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng ph&#7843;i t&#7841;o k&ecirc;nh Youtube. m&#7895;i 1 k&ecirc;nh Youtube s&#7869; &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n cho 1 c&aacute;c nh&acirc;n, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c. Tr&ecirc;n k&ecirc;nh Youtube b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; qu&#7843;n l&yacute; t&#7845;t c&#7843; video v&agrave; n&#7897;i dung &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#259;ng t&#7843;i l&ecirc;n, t&ecirc;n c&#7911;a k&ecirc;nh s&#7869; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; khi b&#7841;n comment, like&hellip; &#7903; c&aacute;c k&ecirc;nh Youtube kh&aacute;c. N&oacute;i chung k&ecirc;nh Youtube c&#361;ng gi&#7889;ng nh&#432; m&#7897;t t&agrave;i kho&#7843;n Facebook v&#7853;y.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 2pt;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/post/109/cach-tao-kenh-youtube1-tdn.jpg\" data-filename=\"cach-tao-kenh-youtube(1).jpg\" style=\"width: 700px;\" loading=\"lazy\"><br></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.8; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 2pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-5d5d8fd1-7fff-773d-236e-0ebdf700665c\"></span></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.7999999999999998;text-align: center;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:2pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Youtube hi&#7879;n nay &#273;ang l&agrave; n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng ki&#7871;m t&#7915; Video s&#7889; 1 th&#7871; gi&#7899;i</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.7999999999999998;text-align: justify;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:2pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">&#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t l&agrave; khi k&ecirc;nh Youtube &#273;&#7911; &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n c&oacute; th&#7875; b&#7853;t t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng ki&#7871;m ti&#7873;n v&agrave; &#273;a s&#7889; ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng &#273;&#7873;u mu&#7889;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng ki&#7871;m ti&#7873;n n&agrave;y c&#7911;a k&ecirc;nh. Nh&#432;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c ti&ecirc;n b&#7841;n ph&#7843;i t&#7841;o k&ecirc;nh Youtube tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&atilde;.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.7999999999999998;text-align: justify;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:2pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i, k&ecirc;nh Youtube c&oacute; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng truy&#7873;n th&ocirc;ng, marketing c&#7921;c k&#7923; hi&#7879;u qu&#7843;. &#272;&acirc;y l&agrave; c&#7847;u n&#7889;i gi&#7919;a ng&#432;&#7901;i xem (kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng) v&#7899;i th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u. Ch&iacute;nh v&igrave; v&#7853;y, vi&#7879;c t&#7841;o k&ecirc;nh Youtube h&#7871;t s&#7913;c c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t n&#7871;u b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u, mu&#7889;n th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng bi&#7871;t &#273;&#7871;n m&#7897;t c&aacute;ch r&#7897;ng r&atilde;i nh&#7845;t.&nbsp;</span></p><h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.7999999999999998;text-align: justify;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:2pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">2. C&aacute;ch t&#7841;o k&ecirc;nh Youtube m&#7899;i nh&#7845;t 2021</span></h2><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.7999999999999998;text-align: justify;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:2pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">&#272;&#7875; c&oacute; th&#7875; t&#7841;o k&ecirc;nh Youtube b&#7841;n th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n theo c&aacute;c b&#432;&#7899;c h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n sau &#273;&acirc;y:</span></p><h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.7999999999999998;text-align: justify;mar