(141, 'vi', 'Hướng dẫn cách đăng video lên Youtube được nhiều lượt xem đề xuất', '/images/upload/post/141/seo-youtube-ntc.png', 'huong-dan-cach-dang-video-len-youtube-duoc-nhieu-luot-xem-de-xuat', '<p>&#272;&#7875; &#273;&#259;ng video l&ecirc;n YouTube v&agrave; t&#7889;i &#432;u h&oacute;a n&oacute; &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7873; xu&#7845;t cho nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i xem h&#417;n, b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; tu&acirc;n theo c&aacute;c b&#432;&#7899;c sau:<p>1. &#272;&#259;ng nh&#7853;p v&agrave;o t&agrave;i kho&#7843;n YouTube: Tr&#432;&#7899;c ti&ecirc;n, h&atilde;y &#273;&#259;ng nh&#7853;p v&agrave;o t&agrave;i kho&#7843;n Google c&#7911;a b&#7841;n (ho&#7863;c t&#7841;o m&#7897;t t&agrave;i kho&#7843;n Google n&#7871;u b&#7841;n ch&#432;a c&oacute;) v&agrave; sau &#273;&oacute; truy c&#7853;p trang web YouTube.</p><p>2. T&#7843;i l&ecirc;n video: B&#7845;m v&agrave;o bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng m&aacute;y &#7843;nh &#7903; g&oacute;c tr&ecirc;n c&ugrave;ng b&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i v&agrave; ch&#7885;n \"T&#7843;i l&ecirc;n video.\" Ch&#7885;n video b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n &#273;&#259;ng l&ecirc;n t&#7915; m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh c&#7911;a b&#7841;n.</p><p><br></p><p>3. T&ugrave;y ch&#7881;nh c&agrave;i &#273;&#7863;t video:</p><ul><li>Ti&ecirc;u &#273;&#7873;: &#272;&#7863;t m&#7897;t ti&ecirc;u &#273;&#7873; h&#7845;p d&#7851;n v&agrave; li&ecirc;n quan &#273;&#7871;n n&#7897;i dung video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n.</li><li>M&ocirc; t&#7843;: Vi&#7871;t m&ocirc; t&#7843; chi ti&#7871;t v&#7873; video, bao g&#7891;m t&#7915; kh&oacute;a li&ecirc;n quan v&agrave; th&ocirc;ng tin h&#7919;u &iacute;ch.</li><li>Th&#7867;: Th&ecirc;m c&aacute;c t&#7915; kh&oacute;a li&ecirc;n quan m&agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i xem c&oacute; th&#7875; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7875; t&igrave;m ki&#7871;m video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n.</li><li>Th&ocirc;ng tin b&#7893; sung: &#272;i&#7873;n th&ocirc;ng tin v&#7873; video nh&#432; danh m&#7909;c, ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919;, v&agrave; th&#7901;i l&#432;&#7907;ng.&nbsp;</li></ul><p style=\"text-align: center; \"><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \"><img src=\"/images/upload/post/141/seo-youtube-jwj.png\" data-filename=\"seo-youtube.png\" style=\"width: 600px;\" loading=\"lazy\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \"><br></p><p>4. Ch&#7885;n c&agrave;i &#273;&#7863;t ri&ecirc;ng t&#432;: B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; ch&#7885;n gi&#7919; video l&agrave; ri&ecirc;ng t&#432; ho&#7863;c c&ocirc;ng khai. &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i m&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u &#273;&#7873; xu&#7845;t, h&atilde;y ch&#7885;n \"C&ocirc;ng khai.\"</p><p>5. T&#7889;i &#432;u h&oacute;a miniatures (h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh b&igrave;a): H&atilde;y ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh b&igrave;a h&#7845;p d&#7851;n &#273;&#7875; thu h&uacute;t s&#7921; ch&uacute; &yacute; c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i xem khi h&#7885; th&#7845;y video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n tr&ecirc;n YouTube.</p><p>6. Th&ecirc;m video v&agrave;o playlist: T&#7841;o playlist cho video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n ho&#7863;c th&ecirc;m video v&agrave;o playlist hi&#7879;n c&oacute; n&#7871;u c&oacute; th&#7875; li&ecirc;n quan.</p><p><br></p><p>7. Ch&#7885;n lo&#7841;i thu&#7897;c t&iacute;nh v&agrave; gi&#7845;y ph&eacute;p: Ch&#7885;n li&#7879;u video c&oacute; d&agrave;nh cho tr&#7867; em hay kh&ocirc;ng, c&#361;ng nh&#432; xem x&eacute;t gi&#7845;y ph&eacute;p video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n.</p><p>8. Th&ecirc;m video v&agrave;o th&#432; vi&#7879;n: B&#7845;m \"&#272;&#259;ng video\" &#273;&#7875; t&#7843;i l&ecirc;n video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n l&ecirc;n YouTube.</p><p>9. T&#7889;i &#432;u h&oacute;a SEO: Sau khi video &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#259;ng, b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; t&#7889;i &#432;u h&oacute;a video c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng t&#7915; kh&oacute;a, th&#7867;, m&ocirc; t&#7843; v&agrave; h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh b&igrave;a li&ecirc;n quan &#273;&#7871;n n&#7897;i dung video. H&atilde;y t&#7841;o ti&ecirc;u &#273;&#7873; v&agrave; m&ocirc; t&#7843; m&ocirc; t&#7843; ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c n&#7897;i dung video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n &#273;&#7875; gi&uacute;p YouTube hi&#7875;u r&otilde; v&agrave; &#273;&#7873; xu&#7845;t video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n cho nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i quan t&acirc;m.</p><p><br></p><p>10. T&#432;&#417;ng t&aacute;c v&#7899;i c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng: Tham gia v&agrave;o cu&#7897;c tr&ograve; chuy&#7879;n v&#7899;i ng&#432;&#7901;i xem, h&#7887;i &yacute; ki&#7871;n, v&agrave; t&#432;&#417;ng t&aacute;c tr&ecirc;n m&#7841;ng x&atilde; h&#7897;i &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o s&#7921; tham gia v&agrave; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng xung quanh k&ecirc;nh c&#7911;a b&#7841;n.</p><p>11. Theo d&otilde;i hi&#7879;u su&#7845;t: Theo d&otilde;i c&aacute;c s&#7889; li&#7879;u th&#7889;ng k&ecirc; tr&ecirc;n YouTube Analytics &#273;&#7875; hi&#7875;u c&aacute;ch video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng v&agrave; &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh chi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;c c&#7911;a b&#7841;n theo &#273;&uacute;ng h&#432;&#7899;ng.</p><p>Nh&#7899; r&#7857;ng, x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng m&#7897;t k&ecirc;nh YouTube ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7873; xu&#7845;t &#273;&ograve;i h&#7887;i th&#7901;i gian v&agrave; c&ocirc;ng s&#7913;c. H&atilde;y ki&ecirc;n nh&#7851;n v&agrave; ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c t&#7841;o ra n&#7897;i dung ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;&#7875; thu h&uacute;t ng&#432;&#7901;i xem v&agrave; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n k&ecirc;nh c&#7911;a b&#7841;n.</p><p></p></p>\n', 1, '2023-11-06 09:16:04', '2023-11-06 09:16:57'),
(142, 'vi', 'Hướng dẫn cách đăng video tiktok tương tác cao đề xuất tốt', '/images/upload/post/142/tang-tuong-tac-tiktok-lpl.jpg', 'huong-dan-cach-dang-video-tiktok-tuong-tac-cao-de-xuat-tot', '<p>&#272;&#7875; &#273;&#259;ng video TikTok &#273;&#7875; t&#259;ng t&#432;&#417;ng t&aacute;c v&agrave; &#273;&#7873; xu&#7845;t t&#7889;t, b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; tu&acirc;n theo c&aacute;c b&#432;&#7899;c v&agrave; chi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;c sau:<ol><li>Ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t ch&#7911; &#273;&#7873; h&#7845;p d&#7851;n: Ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t ch&#7911; &#273;&#7873; ho&#7863;c &yacute; t&#432;&#7903;ng video m&agrave; b&#7841;n ngh&#297; r&#7857;ng s&#7869; g&acirc;y s&#7921; ch&uacute; &yacute; v&agrave; t&#432;&#417;ng t&aacute;c cao. &#272;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y c&oacute; th&#7875; l&agrave; th&aacute;ch th&#7913;c, h&agrave;i h&#432;&#7899;c, s&aacute;ng t&#7841;o ho&#7863;c b&#7845;t k&#7923; &#273;i&#7873;u g&igrave; &#273;ang tr&#7903; n&ecirc;n ph&#7893; bi&#7871;n tr&ecirc;n TikTok.</li><li>S&#7917; d&#7909;ng &acirc;m nh&#7841;c ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p: Ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t b&#7843;n nh&#7841;c ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i n&#7897;i dung video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n. &Acirc;m nh&#7841;c c&oacute; th&#7875; l&agrave; m&#7897;t y&#7871;u t&#7889; quan tr&#7885;ng &#273;&#7875; thu h&uacute;t ng&#432;&#7901;i xem v&agrave; l&agrave;m cho video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n th&uacute; v&#7883; h&#417;n.</li><li>S&aacute;ng t&#7841;o v&agrave; &#273;&#7897;c &#273;&aacute;o: H&atilde;y t&#7841;o ra n&#7897;i dung video s&aacute;ng t&#7841;o v&agrave; &#273;&#7897;c &#273;&aacute;o. &#272;&#7915;ng s&#7907; th&#7917; nghi&#7879;m c&aacute;c &yacute; t&#432;&#7903;ng m&#7899;i v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng gi&#7889;ng ai kh&aacute;c &#273;&#7875; thu h&uacute;t s&#7921; ch&uacute; &yacute;.</li><li>S&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&aacute;c hi&#7879;u &#7913;ng v&agrave; t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng TikTok: S&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&aacute;c hi&#7879;u &#7913;ng, b&#7897; l&#7885;c v&agrave; t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng TikTok &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m cho video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n th&uacute; v&#7883; v&agrave; &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t. TikTok cung c&#7845;p nhi&#7873;u c&ocirc;ng c&#7909; s&aacute;ng t&#7841;o &#273;&#7875; b&#7841;n t&#7841;o ra n&#7897;i dung &#273;&#7897;c &#273;&aacute;o.</li><li>Gi&#7919; video ng&#7855;n g&#7885;n: L&#432;u &yacute; r&#7857;ng video TikTok th&#432;&#7901;ng ng&#7855;n, th&#432;&#7901;ng t&#7915; 15 gi&acirc;y &#273;&#7871;n 60 gi&acirc;y. H&atilde;y gi&#7919; video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n ng&#7855;n g&#7885;n v&agrave; g&#7885;n l&#7865; &#273;&#7875; gi&#7919; s&#7921; ch&uacute; &yacute; c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i xem.</li><li>S&#7917; d&#7909;ng ph&ocirc;ng n&#7873;n v&agrave; &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng t&#7889;t: &#272;&#7843;m b&#7843;o r&#7857;ng video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n c&oacute; &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng t&#7889;t v&agrave; m&#7897;t ph&ocirc;ng n&#7873;n s&#7841;ch s&#7869; v&agrave; h&#7845;p d&#7851;n.</li><li>T&#7889;i &#432;u h&oacute;a ti&ecirc;u &#273;&#7873; v&agrave; m&ocirc; t&#7843;: S&#7917; d&#7909;ng m&#7897;t ti&ecirc;u &#273;&#7873; m&ocirc; t&#7843; n&#7897;i dung video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n v&agrave; th&ecirc;m c&aacute;c t&#7915; kh&oacute;a li&ecirc;n quan &#273;&#7875; gi&uacute;p ng&#432;&#7901;i xem t&igrave;m ki&#7871;m video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n d&#7877; d&agrave;ng h&#417;n.</li><li>S&#7917; d&#7909;ng hashtag ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p: Th&ecirc;m c&aacute;c hashtag ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&agrave;o m&ocirc; t&#7843; video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n &#273;&#7875; t&#259;ng kh&#7843; n&#259;ng t&igrave;m th&#7845;y video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n tr&ecirc;n TikTok.</li><li>T&#432;&#417;ng t&aacute;c v&#7899;i c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng: H&atilde;y t&#432;&#417;ng t&aacute;c v&#7899;i ng&#432;&#7901;i xem b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch tr&#7843; l&#7901;i b&igrave;nh lu&#7853;n v&agrave; t&#432;&#417;ng t&aacute;c v&#7899;i video c&#7911;a h&#7885;. &#272;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y c&oacute; th&#7875; gi&uacute;p t&#7841;o s&#7921; k&#7871;t n&#7889;i v&agrave; th&uacute;c &#273;&#7849;y t&#432;&#417;ng t&aacute;c.</li><li>Theo d&otilde;i hi&#7879;u su&#7845;t: S&#7917; d&#7909;ng ph&#7847;n th&#7889;ng k&ecirc; TikTok &#273;&#7875; theo d&otilde;i hi&#7879;u su&#7845;t c&#7911;a video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n v&agrave; &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh chi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;c c&#7911;a b&#7841;n d&#7921;a tr&ecirc;n d&#7919; li&#7879;u.</li></ol><p>Nh&#7899; r&#7857;ng TikTok l&agrave; m&#7897;t n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng x&atilde; h&#7897;i v&#7899;i nhi&#7873;u th&aacute;ch th&#7913;c, v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; c&aacute;ch ch&#7855;c ch&#7855;n &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7841;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#432;&#417;ng t&aacute;c cao. H&atilde;y ki&ecirc;n nh&#7851;n v&agrave; ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c th&#7917; nghi&#7879;m v&agrave; c&#7843;i thi&#7879;n n&#7897;i dung c&#7911;a b&#7841;n &#273;&#7875; thu h&uacute;t m&#7897;t l&#432;&#7907;ng l&#7899;n ng&#432;&#7901;i xem.</p></p>\n', 1, '2023-11-06 10:34:23', '2023-11-06 10:34:23'),
(143, 'vi', 'Hướng dẫn cách tăng sub cho kênh youtube', '/images/upload/post/143/cach-tang-sub-youtube-xrt.jpg', 'huong-dan-cach-tang-sub-cho-kenh-youtube', '<p>Vi&#7879;c t&#259;ng s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; (subscribers) cho k&ecirc;nh YouTube y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u th&#7901;i gian, c&ocirc;ng s&#7913;c v&agrave; chi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;c. D&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y l&agrave; m&#7897;t s&#7889; c&aacute;ch b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; th&#7917; &#273;&#7875; t&#259;ng s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng sub cho k&ecirc;nh c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh<ol><li>T&#7841;o n&#7897;i dung ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng: N&#7897;i dung l&agrave; y&#7871;u t&#7889; quan tr&#7885;ng nh&#7845;t &#273;&#7875; thu h&uacute;t v&agrave; gi&#7919; ch&acirc;n ng&#432;&#7901;i xem. H&atilde;y &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o r&#7857;ng video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n th&uacute; v&#7883;, h&#7919;u &iacute;ch v&agrave; c&oacute; gi&aacute; tr&#7883; cho ng&#432;&#7901;i xem.</li><li>Th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n t&#7841;o video: M&#7897;t l&#7883;ch t&#7841;o video &#273;&#7873;u &#273;&#7863;n gi&uacute;p ng&#432;&#7901;i xem bi&#7871;t r&#7857;ng k&ecirc;nh c&#7911;a b&#7841;n lu&ocirc;n c&oacute; n&#7897;i dung m&#7899;i v&agrave; th&uacute; v&#7883;. Th&#7917; c&#7889; g&#7855;ng duy tr&igrave; m&#7897;t t&#7847;n su&#7845;t &#273;&#259;ng video &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh.</li><li>Ch&#7885;n ch&#7911; &#273;&#7873; m&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u: Ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t ch&#7911; &#273;&#7873; ho&#7863;c l&#297;nh v&#7921;c c&#7909; th&#7875; cho k&ecirc;nh c&#7911;a b&#7841;n &#273;&#7875; t&#7853;p trung v&agrave; thu h&uacute;t m&#7897;t &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng m&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u.</li><li>S&#7917; d&#7909;ng t&#7915; kh&oacute;a: T&igrave;m hi&#7875;u v&#7873; t&#7915; kh&oacute;a li&ecirc;n quan &#273;&#7871;n n&#7897;i dung c&#7911;a b&#7841;n v&agrave; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ch&uacute;ng trong ti&ecirc;u &#273;&#7873;, m&ocirc; t&#7843; v&agrave; th&#7867; c&#7911;a video &#273;&#7875; t&#7889;i &#432;u h&oacute;a SEO v&agrave; gi&uacute;p ng&#432;&#7901;i xem t&igrave;m th&#7845;y video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n d&#7877; d&agrave;ng h&#417;n.</li><li>T&#7841;o h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u: T&#7841;o m&#7897;t h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh n&#7873;n, h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n v&agrave; logo th&#7875; hi&#7879;n t&iacute;nh nh&#7845;t qu&aacute;n tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n b&#7897; k&ecirc;nh c&#7911;a b&#7841;n.</li><li>Khuy&#7871;n m&atilde;i tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c m&#7841;ng x&atilde; h&#7897;i: Chia s&#7867; video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c m&#7841;ng x&atilde; h&#7897;i kh&aacute;c nh&#432; Facebook, Twitter v&agrave; Instagram &#273;&#7875; thu h&uacute;t ng&#432;&#7901;i xem t&#7915; nhi&#7873;u n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng kh&aacute;c nhau.</li><li>H&#7907;p t&aacute;c v&#7899;i c&aacute;c YouTuber kh&aacute;c: Khi b&#7841;n h&#7907;p t&aacute;c v&#7899;i c&aacute;c YouTuber kh&aacute;c ho&#7863;c tham gia v&agrave;o c&aacute;c video chung, b&#7841;n c&oacute; c&#417; h&#7897;i ti&#7871;p c&#7853;n m&#7897;t l&#432;&#7907;ng l&#7899;n ng&#432;&#7901;i xem m&#7899;i.</li><li>T&#432;&#417;ng t&aacute;c v&#7899;i c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng: T&#432;&#417;ng t&aacute;c v&#7899;i ng&#432;&#7901;i xem c&#7911;a b&#7841;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch tr&#7843; l&#7901;i b&igrave;nh lu&#7853;n, h&#7887;i &yacute; ki&#7871;n, v&agrave; t&#7841;o s&#7921; k&#7871;t n&#7889;i v&#7899;i h&#7885;.</li><li>S&#7917; d&#7909;ng cu&#7897;c thi v&agrave; qu&agrave; t&#7863;ng: T&#7893; ch&#7913;c cu&#7897;c thi ho&#7863;c t&#7863;ng qu&agrave; cho ng&#432;&#7901;i xem c&oacute; th&#7875; l&agrave;m t&#259;ng s&#7921; quan t&acirc;m &#273;&#7871;n k&ecirc;nh c&#7911;a b&#7841;n.</li><li>Theo d&otilde;i hi&#7879;u su&#7845;t: S&#7917; d&#7909;ng YouTube Analytics &#273;&#7875; theo d&otilde;i hi&#7879;u su&#7845;t c&#7911;a k&ec