71;t Lu&#7853;n:</span>\r\nKi&#7871;m ti&#7873;n tr&ecirc;n YouTube c&oacute; th&#7875; th&uacute; v&#7883; v&agrave; &#273;&#7847;y tri&#7875;n v&#7885;ng n&#7871;u b&#7841;n ch&uacute; t&acirc;m v&agrave; theo d&otilde;i nh&#7919;ng b&#432;&#7899;c t&#7889;i &#432;u h&oacute;a n&ecirc;u tr&ecirc;n. H&atilde;y nh&#7899; r&#7857;ng vi&#7879;c x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng m&#7897;t k&ecirc;nh YouTube th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng &#273;&ograve;i h&#7887;i ki&ecirc;n nh&#7851;n v&agrave; c&#7889;ng hi&#7871;n, nh&#432;ng n&oacute; c&oacute; th&#7875; bi&#7871;n &#273;am m&ecirc; c&#7911;a b&#7841;n th&agrave;nh ngu&#7891;n thu nh&#7853;p &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh.</p><p><br></p></p>\n', 1, '2023-11-06 11:06:03', '2023-11-06 11:06:04');
