(146, 'vi', 'Hướng Dẫn Chi Tiết Cách Bắt Đầu Kiếm Tiền Trên YouTube Và Xây Dựng Kênh Youtube', '/images/upload/post/146/bat-kiem-tien-youtube-tio.png', 'huong-dan-chi-tiet-cach-bat-dau-kiem-tien-tren-youtube-va-xay-dung-kenh-youtube', '<p>YouTube kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7881; l&agrave; m&#7897;t n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng chia s&#7867; video n&#7893;i ti&#7871;ng m&agrave; c&ograve;n l&agrave; c&#417; h&#7897;i tuy&#7879;t v&#7901;i &#273;&#7875; ki&#7871;m ti&#7873;n v&agrave; x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng tr&#7921;c tuy&#7871;n c&#7911;a b&#7841;n. B&agrave;i vi&#7871;t n&agrave;y s&#7869; h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n b&#7841;n t&#7915;ng b&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7875; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u ki&#7871;m ti&#7873;n tr&ecirc;n YouTube v&agrave; x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng k&ecirc;nh ph&aacute;t s&oacute;ng th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng.<p><br></p><p><b>B&#432;&#7899;c 1: T&#7841;o K&ecirc;nh YouTube</b></p><p>&#272;&#259;ng nh&#7853;p v&agrave;o t&agrave;i kho&#7843;n Google c&#7911;a b&#7841;n v&agrave; t&#7841;o k&ecirc;nh YouTube. Ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t t&ecirc;n k&ecirc;nh ph&#7843;n &aacute;nh n&#7897;i dung b&#7841;n s&#7869; chia s&#7867; v&agrave; t&#7889;i &#432;u h&oacute;a h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n v&agrave; b&igrave;a k&ecirc;nh.</p><p><br></p><p><b>B&#432;&#7899;c 2: N&#7897;i Dung Ch&#7845;t L&#432;&#7907;ng</b></p><p>T&#7841;o n&#7897;i dung ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng, h&#7845;p d&#7851;n v&agrave; &#273;&#7897;c &#273;&aacute;o. Ch&#7885;n l&#297;nh v&#7921;c m&agrave; b&#7841;n &#273;am m&ecirc; v&agrave; c&oacute; ki&#7871;n th&#7913;c chuy&ecirc;n s&acirc;u. Video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n n&ecirc;n gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; ho&#7863;c mang l&#7841;i gi&aacute; tr&#7883; cho ng&#432;&#7901;i xem.</p><p><br></p><p><b>B&#432;&#7899;c 3: Tham Gia Ch&#432;&#417;ng Tr&igrave;nh &#272;&#7889;i T&aacute;c YouTube (YPP)</b></p><p>&#272;&#7843;m b&#7843;o r&#7857;ng b&#7841;n &#273;&aacute;p &#7913;ng &#273;&#7911; y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u tham gia YPP, bao g&#7891;m &iacute;t nh&#7845;t 1.000 ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; v&agrave; 4.000 gi&#7901; xem trong 12 th&aacute;ng g&#7847;n &#273;&acirc;y. Sau khi &#273;&#7841;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y, &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; tham gia YPP &#273;&#7875; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u ki&#7871;m ti&#7873;n t&#7915; qu&#7843;ng c&aacute;o tr&ecirc;n video c&#7911;a b&#7841;n.</p><p><br></p><p><b>B&#432;&#7899;c 4: K&#7871;t N&#7889;i T&agrave;i Kho&#7843;n AdSense</b></p><p>Li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t t&agrave;i kho&#7843;n AdSense c&#7911;a b&#7841;n v&#7899;i k&ecirc;nh YouTube &#273;&#7875; nh&#7853;n thanh to&aacute;n. AdSense s&#7869; qu&#7843;n l&yacute; doanh thu qu&#7843;ng c&aacute;o v&agrave; chuy&#7875;n kho&#7843;n ti&#7873;n v&agrave;o t&agrave;i kho&#7843;n c&#7911;a b&#7841;n.</p><p><br></p><p><b>B&#432;&#7899;c 5: T&#7889;i &#431;u H&oacute;a Video</b></p><p>T&#7921;a &#273;&#7873; v&agrave; m&ocirc; t&#7843;: S&#7917; d&#7909;ng t&#7921;a &#273;&#7873; v&agrave; m&ocirc; t&#7843; ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c, h&#7845;p d&#7851;n, v&agrave; c&oacute; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng.</p><p>Th&#7867; (tags): Th&ecirc;m th&#7867; ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p &#273;&#7875; t&#259;ng kh&#7843; n&#259;ng xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n c&#7911;a video trong k&#7871;t qu&#7843; t&igrave;m ki&#7871;m.</p><p><b>B&#432;&#7899;c 6: X&acirc;y D&#7921;ng C&#7897;ng &#272;&#7891;ng</b></p><p>T&#432;&#417;ng t&aacute;c v&#7899;i ng&#432;&#7901;i xem th&ocirc;ng qua b&igrave;nh lu&#7853;n v&agrave; c&aacute;c m&#7841;ng x&atilde; h&#7897;i. &#272;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i, th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n c&#7853;p nh&#7853;t n&#7897;i dung m&#7899;i &#273;&#7875; gi&#7919; cho c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n lu&ocirc;n quan t&acirc;m.</p><p><br></p><p><b>B&#432;&#7899;c 7: Theo D&otilde;i Th&#7889;ng K&ecirc; v&agrave; Ph&#7843;n H&#7891;i</b></p><p>S&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng c&#7909; th&#7889;ng k&ecirc; c&#7911;a YouTube &#273;&#7875; theo d&otilde;i hi&#7879;u su&#7845;t video v&agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i xem. Ch&uacute; &yacute; &#273;&#7871;n ph&#7843;n h&#7891;i &#273;&#7875; c&#7843;i thi&#7879;n n&#7897;i dung c&#7911;a b&#7841;n.</p><p><br></p><p><b>K&#7871;t Lu&#7853;n</b></p><p>B&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch tu&acirc;n th&#7911; nh&#7919;ng b&#432;&#7899;c tr&ecirc;n v&agrave; ki&ecirc;n nh&#7851;n, b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u ki&#7871;m ti&#7873;n tr&ecirc;n YouTube v&agrave; x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng m&#7897;t k&ecirc;nh ph&aacute;t s&oacute;ng th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng. H&atilde;y nh&#7899; r&#7857;ng s&#7921; ki&ecirc;n tr&igrave; v&agrave; s&aacute;ng t&#7841;o s&#7869; l&agrave; ch&igrave;a kh&oacute;a &#273;&#7875; thu h&uacute;t v&agrave; gi&#7919; ch&acirc;n ng&#432;&#7901;i xem c&#7911;a b&#7841;n. Ch&uacute;c b&#7841;n th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng tr&ecirc;n h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh YouTube c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh!</p></p>\n', 1, '2023-12-01 01:53:37', '2023-12-01 01:53:38'),
(147, 'vi', 'Bảng giá dịch vụ mua bán SubYoutube uy tín mới nhất 2025', '/images/upload/post/147/sub-olp.jpg', 'bang-gia-dich-vu-mua-ban-subyoutube-uy-tin-moi-nhat-2025', '<p>Xin ch&agrave;o c&aacute;c b&#7841;n d&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y l&agrave; b&#7843;ng gi&aacute; d&#7883;ch v&#7909; mua b&aacute;n SubYoutube . Do ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch c&#7911;a Goo-gle n&ecirc;n m&igrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng ti&#7879;n tr&igrave;nh b&agrave;y nhi&#7873;u ch&#7881; &#273;&#7875; b&#7843;ng gi&aacute; cho m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i tham kh&#7843;o. Li&ecirc;n h&#7879; zalo 0899.707.888 &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#432; v&#7845;n.<p><br></p><table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><tbody><tr><td>L&#432;&#7907;ng Sub</td><td>Gi&aacute;</td><td>Th&#7901;i gian ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh</td><td>L&#432;&#7907;ng sub t&#7889;i &#273;a 1 l&#7847;n ch&#7841;y</td></tr><tr><td>1000</td><td>1.000.000</td><td>2-3 ng&agrave;y</td><td>1000</td></tr><tr><td><p>\r\n<br></p></td><td></td><td></td><td><br></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Quy tr&igrave;nh:</p><p>1. K&#7871;t b&#7841;n Zalo 0899707888</p><p>2. G&#7917;i link k&ecirc;nh Youtube c&#7847;n ch&#7841;y cho Youtubestore.vn ( Kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n g&#7917;i email + m&#7853;t kh&#7849;u)</p><p>3. Thanh to&aacute;n chi ph&iacute;</p><p>4. Youtubestore.vn s&#7869; tri&#7875;n khai v&agrave; setup</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></p>\n', 1, '2024-11-24 03:05:34', '2025-11-22 11:18:42'),
(148, 'vi', 'Dịch Vụ Tăng Follow TikTok – Giải Pháp Hiệu Quả Để Phát Triển Kênh TikTok Của Bạn', '/images/upload/post/148/tang-follow-tik-tok-loi-ich-vnu.png', 'dich-vu-tang-follow-tiktok-giai-phap-hieu-qua-de-phat-trien-kenh-tiktok-cua-ban', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">B&#7843;ng gi&aacute;:</span><table class=\"table table-bordered\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\">&#272;&#417;n gi&aacute; t&#7889;i thi&#7875;u 1000 follow tiktok</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">T&#7889;i &#273;a follow</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">1 ng&agrave;y ch&#7841;y t&#7889;i &#273;a follow</td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\">120k 1000 follow&nbsp;</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">100.000 folow</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">10.000</td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\">150k 1000 follow</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">500.000 folow</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">50.000</td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\">170k 1000 folow</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">1.000.000 folow</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">5000-10.000</td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\">200k 1000 folow</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">10.000.000 folow</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">50.000</td></tr></tbody></table><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">TikTok hi&#7879;n nay l&agrave; m&#7897;t n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng m&#7841;ng x&atilde; h&#7897;i h&agrave;ng &#273;&#7847;u, thu h&uacute;t h&agrave;ng tri&#7879;u ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng m&#7895;i ng&agrave;y. V&#7899;i s&#7921; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n nhanh ch&oacute;ng, vi&#7879;c s&#7903; h&#7919;u m&#7897;t k&ecirc;nh TikTok c&oacute; l&#432;&#7907;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i theo d&otilde;i l&#7899;n kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7881; gi&uacute;p b&#7841;n x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u c&aacute; nh&acirc;n, m&agrave; c&ograve;n m&#7903; ra c&#417; h&#7897;i kinh doanh v&agrave; h&#7907;p t&aacute;c v&#7899;i nhi&#7873;u nh&atilde;n h&agrave;ng. Tuy n