(158, 'vi', 'Hướng dẫn làm YouTube trên điện thoại kiếm 80 - 100 triệu/tháng', '/images/upload/post/158/kiem-tien-youtube-n9w.jpg', 'huong-dan-lam-youtube-tren-dien-thoai-kiem-80-100-trieuthang', '<h2 data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">1. T&#7841;i sao l&agrave;m YouTube tr&ecirc;n &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i l&agrave; xu h&#432;&#7899;ng hi&#7879;n nay?</span><h4><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Ng&agrave;y nay, vi&#7879;c l&agrave;m YouTube kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n gi&#7899;i h&#7841;n tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c thi&#7871;t b&#7883; chuy&ecirc;n nghi&#7879;p nh&#432; m&aacute;y quay hay m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh. &#272;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i th&ocirc;ng minh &#273;ang tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng c&#7909; &#273;&#7855;c l&#7921;c gi&uacute;p m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i d&#7877; d&agrave;ng s&aacute;ng t&#7841;o n&#7897;i dung v&agrave; ki&#7871;m ti&#7873;n tr&ecirc;n YouTube. V&#7899;i ch&#7881; m&#7897;t chi&#7871;c &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i, b&#7841;n ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n c&oacute; th&#7875; quay, ch&#7881;nh s&#7917;a v&agrave; &#273;&#259;ng t&#7843;i video &#273;&#7875; x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng k&ecirc;nh c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh.</span></h4><h3 class=\"dropdown-item\" id=\"loi-ich-cua-viec-lam-youtube-tren-dien-thoai\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">L&#7907;i &iacute;ch c&#7911;a vi&#7879;c l&agrave;m YouTube tr&ecirc;n &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i:</span></h3><ul data-spread=\"false\"><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Chi ph&iacute; th&#7845;p:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"> Kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; m&aacute;y m&oacute;c &#273;&#7855;t ti&#7873;n.</span></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Ti&#7879;n l&#7907;i:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"> Quay video m&#7885;i l&uacute;c, m&#7885;i n&#417;i.</span></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">D&#7877; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"> C&aacute;c &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng ch&#7881;nh s&#7917;a tr&ecirc;n &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng th&acirc;n thi&#7879;n.</span></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">T&#259;ng t&#7889;c &#273;&#7897; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t n&#7897;i dung:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"> Qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh t&#7915; quay &#273;&#7871;n &#273;&#259;ng t&#7843;i c&oacute; th&#7875; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n nhanh ch&oacute;ng.</span></p></li></ul><div><hr></div><h2><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">2. C&#7847;n chu&#7849;n b&#7883; nh&#7919;ng g&igrave; &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m YouTube tr&ecirc;n &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i?</span></h2><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">&#272;&#7875; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u, b&#7841;n c&#7847;n:</span></p><h3 id=\"a-thiet-bi-can-thiet\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">a) Thi&#7871;t b&#7883; c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t:</span></h3><ul data-spread=\"false\"><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">&#272;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i th&ocirc;ng minh:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"> Ch&#7885;n &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i c&oacute; camera ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng (t&#7889;t nh&#7845;t t&#7915; 1080p tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n).</span></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Mic thu &acirc;m:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"> &#272;&#7875; t&#259;ng ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng &acirc;m thanh, b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; mic r&#7901;i nh&#432; Boya BY-M1 ho&#7863;c Rode Wireless Go.</span></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Gimbal ho&#7863;c tripod:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"> Gi&uacute;p quay video &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh, tr&aacute;nh rung l&#7855;c.</span></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">&#272;&egrave;n chi&#7871;u s&aacute;ng:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"> Nh&#432; &#273;&egrave;n ring light &#273;&#7875; c&#7843;i thi&#7879;n &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng khi quay trong nh&agrave;.</span></p></li></ul><h3 id=\"b-ung-dung-ho-tro\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">b) &#7912;ng d&#7909;ng h&#7895; tr&#7907;:</span></h3><ul data-spread=\"false\"><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Quay video:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"> FiLMiC Pro, Open Camera.</span></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Ch&#7881;nh s&#7917;a video:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"> CapCut, Kinemaster, Adobe Premiere Rush.</span></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">T&#7841;o h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh thumbnail:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"> Canva, PicsArt.</span></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch k&ecirc;nh:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"> YouTube Studio, TubeBuddy.</span></p><p><img src=\"/images/upload/post/158/ung-dung-lam-video-x58.jpg\" data-filename=\"ung-dung-lam-video.jpg\" style=\"width: 900px;\" loading=\"lazy\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br></span></p></li></ul><div><hr></div><h2><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">3. C&aacute;c b&#432;&#7899;c x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng k&ecirc;nh YouTube ki&#7871;m 80 tri&#7879;u/th&aacute;ng</span></h2><h3 id=\"buoc-1-chon-linh-vuc-va-doi-tuong-muc-tieu\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">B&#432;&#7899;c 1: Ch&#7885;n l&#297;nh v&#7921;c v&agrave; &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng m&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u</span></h3><ul data-spread=\"false\"><li><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">X&aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh l&#297;nh v&#7921;c m&agrave; b&#7841;n &#273;am m&ecirc;, v&iacute; d&#7909;: &#7849;m th&#7921;c, du l&#7883;ch, c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879;, l&agrave;m &#273;&#7865;p.</span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">T&igrave;m hi&#7875;u &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng xem k&ecirc;nh c&#7911;a b&#7841;n: &#272;&#7897; tu&#7893;i, s&#7903; th&iacute;ch, nhu c&#7847;u.</span></p></li></ul><h3 id=\"buoc-2-len-y-tuong-va-ke-hoach-noi-dung\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">B&#432;&#7899;c 2: L&ecirc;n &yacute; t&#432;&#7903;ng v&agrave; k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch n&#7897;i dung</span></h3><ul data-spread=\"false\"><li><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Nghi&ecirc;n c&#7913;u t&#7915; kh&oacute;a v&#7899;i c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng c&#7909; nh&#432; Google Keyword Planner, Ahrefs.</span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">L&#7853;p danh s&aacute;ch ch&#7911; &#273;&#7873; theo tu&#7847;n/th&aacute;ng.</span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">&#272;&#7843;m b&#7843;o n&#7897;i dung h&#7845;p d&#7851;n, c&oacute; gi&aacute; tr&#7883; cho ng&#432;&#7901;i xem.</span></p></li></ul><h3 id=\"buoc-3-quay-va-chinh-sua-video\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">B&#432;&#7899;c 3: Quay v&agrave; ch&#7881;nh s&#7917;a video</span></h3><ul data-spread=\"false\"><li><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Quay video &#7903; n&#417;i c&oacute; &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng t&#7889;t v&agrave; &acirc;m thanh r&otilde; r&agrave;ng.</span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">S&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&aacute;c hi&#7879;u &#7913;ng, chuy&#7875;n c&#7843;nh, &acirc;m nh&#7841;c ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p &#273;&#7875; t&#259;ng s&#7921; chuy&ecirc;n nghi&#7879;p.</span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Th&ecirc;m ti&ecirc;u &#273;&#7873;, ph&#7909; &#273;&#7873; &#273;&#7875; t&#259;ng t&iacute;nh t&#432;&#417;ng t&aacute;c.</span></p></li></ul><h3 id=\"buoc-4-toi-uu-hoa-seo-cho-video\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">B&#432;&#7899;c 4: T&#7889;i &#432;u h&oacute;a SEO cho video</span></h3><ul data-spread=\"false\"><li><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Ti&ecirc;u &#273;&#7873; h&#7845;p d&#7851;n, ch&#7913;a t&#7915; kh&oacute;a ch&iacute;nh.</span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">M&ocirc; t&#7843; chi ti&#7871;t, ch&egrave;n t&#791