(161, 'vi', 'Tất Tần Tật Về YouTube Shopping Shopee Cho Người Mới', '/images/upload/post/161/youtube-shopping-kn9.png', 'tat-tan-tat-ve-youtube-shopping-shopee-cho-nguoi-moi', '<p data-start=\"290\" data-end=\"601\">Trong th&#7901;i &#273;&#7841;i video l&ecirc;n ng&ocirc;i, <strong data-start=\"321\" data-end=\"348\">YouTube Shopping Shopee</strong> &#273;ang tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh xu h&#432;&#7899;ng b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng online hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i, k&#7871;t h&#7907;p gi&#7919;a s&#7913;c m&#7841;nh c&#7911;a n&#7897;i dung v&agrave; n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i &#273;i&#7879;n t&#7917; h&agrave;ng &#273;&#7847;u &#272;&ocirc;ng Nam &Aacute;. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n l&agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng ho&#7863;c nh&agrave; s&aacute;ng t&#7841;o n&#7897;i dung, &#273;&acirc;y ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; c&#417; h&#7897;i b&#7913;t ph&aacute; doanh s&#7889; m&agrave; b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; b&#7887; qua.<hr data-start=\"603\" data-end=\"606\"><h2 data-start=\"608\" data-end=\"644\">1. YouTube Shopping Shopee l&agrave; g&igrave;?</h2><p data-start=\"646\" data-end=\"929\"><strong data-start=\"646\" data-end=\"673\">YouTube Shopping Shopee</strong> l&agrave; h&igrave;nh th&#7913;c t&iacute;ch h&#7907;p s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m t&#7915; gian h&agrave;ng Shopee tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p v&agrave;o video ho&#7863;c livestream tr&ecirc;n YouTube. Ng&#432;&#7901;i xem c&oacute; th&#7875; b&#7845;m v&agrave;o s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m hi&#7875;n th&#7883; &#273;&#7875; xem chi ti&#7871;t v&agrave; mua h&agrave;ng ngay tr&ecirc;n n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng YouTube, m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i tho&aacute;t ra &#273;&#7875; truy c&#7853;p Shopee th&#7911; c&ocirc;ng.</p><hr data-start=\"931\" data-end=\"934\"><h2 data-start=\"936\" data-end=\"989\">2. L&#7907;i &iacute;ch khi k&#7871;t n&#7889;i YouTube Shopping v&#7899;i Shopee</h2><h3 data-start=\"991\" data-end=\"1019\" id=\"tang-ty-le-chuyen-doi\">&#10004;&#65039; T&#259;ng t&#7927; l&#7879; chuy&#7875;n &#273;&#7893;i</h3><p data-start=\"1021\" data-end=\"1167\">Nh&#7901; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng <strong data-start=\"1034\" data-end=\"1072\">g&#7855;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p trong video</strong>, ng&#432;&#7901;i xem c&oacute; th&#7875; h&agrave;nh &#273;&#7897;ng ngay t&#7913;c th&igrave; khi c&oacute; nhu c&#7847;u, gi&uacute;p gia t&#259;ng t&#7927; l&#7879; mua h&agrave;ng &#273;&aacute;ng k&#7875;.</p><h3 data-start=\"1169\" data-end=\"1200\" id=\"toi-uu-noi-dung-tiep-thi\">&#10004;&#65039; T&#7889;i &#432;u n&#7897;i dung ti&#7871;p th&#7883;</h3><p data-start=\"1202\" data-end=\"1365\">Thay v&igrave; qu&#7843;ng c&aacute;o truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng, b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; t&#7853;n d&#7909;ng <strong data-start=\"1254\" data-end=\"1296\">video review, h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng, unbox</strong>... &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o ni&#7873;m tin v&agrave; k&iacute;ch th&iacute;ch h&agrave;nh vi mua h&agrave;ng m&#7897;t c&aacute;ch t&#7921; nhi&ecirc;n.</p><h3 data-start=\"1367\" data-end=\"1396\" id=\"phat-trien-thuong-hieu\">&#10004;&#65039; Ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u</h3><p data-start=\"1398\" data-end=\"1525\">Khi s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n xuy&ecirc;n su&#7889;t n&#7897;i dung h&#7845;p d&#7851;n tr&ecirc;n YouTube, ng&#432;&#7901;i xem s&#7869; d&#7877; d&agrave;ng ghi nh&#7899; v&agrave; nh&#7853;n di&#7879;n th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u t&#7889;t h&#417;n.</p><p data-start=\"1398\" data-end=\"1525\"><img src=\"/images/upload/post/161/youtube-shopee-uee.png\" data-filename=\"youtube shopee.png\" style=\"width: 800px;\" loading=\"lazy\"><br></p><hr data-start=\"1527\" data-end=\"1530\"><h2 data-start=\"1532\" data-end=\"1579\">3. C&aacute;ch li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t YouTube Shopping v&#7899;i Shopee</h2><p data-start=\"1581\" data-end=\"1670\">&#272;&#7875; thi&#7871;t l&#7853;p t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng <strong data-start=\"1604\" data-end=\"1631\">YouTube Shopping Shopee</strong>, b&#7841;n c&#7847;n th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n m&#7897;t s&#7889; b&#432;&#7899;c c&#417; b&#7843;n:</p><h3 data-start=\"1672\" data-end=\"1723\" id=\"buoc-1-tham-gia-chuong-trinh-youtube-partner\">&#9989; B&#432;&#7899;c 1: Tham gia ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh YouTube Partner</h3><p data-start=\"1725\" data-end=\"1816\">K&ecirc;nh YouTube c&#7911;a b&#7841;n ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7911; &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n b&#7853;t ki&#7871;m ti&#7873;n v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng vi ph&#7841;m ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng.</p><h3 data-start=\"1818\" data-end=\"1868\" id=\"buoc-2-tao-tai-khoan-google-merchant-center\">&#9989; B&#432;&#7899;c 2: T&#7841;o t&agrave;i kho&#7843;n Google Merchant Center</h3><p data-start=\"1870\" data-end=\"1950\">T&agrave;i kho&#7843;n n&agrave;y d&ugrave;ng &#273;&#7875; qu&#7843;n l&yacute; d&#7919; li&#7879;u s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m t&#7915; Shopee v&agrave; k&#7871;t n&#7889;i v&#7899;i YouTube.</p><h3 data-start=\"1952\" data-end=\"1991\" id=\"buoc-3-tich-hop-gian-hang-shopee\">&#9989; B&#432;&#7899;c 3: T&iacute;ch h&#7907;p gian h&agrave;ng Shopee</h3><p data-start=\"1993\" data-end=\"2115\">Th&ocirc;ng qua ngu&#7891;n c&#7845;p d&#7919; li&#7879;u (data feed), API ho&#7863;c n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng &#273;&#7889;i t&aacute;c, b&#7841;n s&#7869; &#273;&#7891;ng b&#7897; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m t&#7915; Shopee l&ecirc;n Merchant Center.</p><h3 data-start=\"2117\" data-end=\"2169\" id=\"buoc-4-gan-san-pham-vao-video-hoac-livestream\">&#9989; B&#432;&#7899;c 4: G&#7855;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m v&agrave;o video ho&#7863;c livestream</h3><p data-start=\"2171\" data-end=\"2291\">Sau khi k&#7871;t n&#7889;i th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng, b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n nh&#7919;ng video mu&#7889;n g&#7855;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m v&agrave; theo d&otilde;i hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng qua b&aacute;o c&aacute;o.</p><p data-start=\"2171\" data-end=\"2291\"><img src=\"/images/upload/post/161/lien-ket-shopee-voi-youtube-ndj.png\" data-filename=\"Li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t shopee v&#7899;i youtube.png\" style=\"width: 800px;\" loading=\"lazy\"><br></p><hr data-start=\"2293\" data-end=\"2296\"><h2 data-start=\"2298\" data-end=\"2340\">4. Ai n&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng YouTube Shopping Shopee?</h2><ul data-start=\"2342\" data-end=\"2596\">\r\n<li data-start=\"2342\" data-end=\"2421\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2344\" data-end=\"2421\">Ng&#432;&#7901;i b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng tr&ecirc;n Shopee mu&#7889;n <strong data-start=\"2376\" data-end=\"2420\">m&#7903; r&#7897;ng k&ecirc;nh b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng qua n&#7897;i dung video</strong>.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2422\" data-end=\"2505\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2424\" data-end=\"2505\">Nh&agrave; s&aacute;ng t&#7841;o n&#7897;i dung (YouTuber) mu&#7889;n <strong data-start=\"2462\" data-end=\"2504\">ki&#7871;m th&ecirc;m thu nh&#7853;p t&#7915; affiliate Shopee</strong>.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2506\" data-end=\"2596\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2508\" data-end=\"2596\">Doanh nghi&#7879;p nh&#7887; ho&#7863;c th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u c&aacute; nh&acirc;n c&#7847;n <strong data-start=\"2554\" data-end=\"2595\">t&#259;ng kh&#7843; n&#259;ng ti&#7871;p c&#7853;n kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng tr&#7867;</strong>.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul><hr data-start=\"2598\" data-end=\"2601\"><h2 data-start=\"2603\" data-end=\"2625\">5. L&#432;u &yacute; quan tr&#7885;ng</h2><ul data-start=\"2627\" data-end=\"2861\">\r\n<li data-start=\"2627\" data-end=\"2774\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2629\" data-end=\"2774\">Hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i, <strong data-start=\"2639\" data-end=\"2696\">YouTube Shopping t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam v&#7851;n &#273;ang tri&#7875;n khai d&#7847;n</strong>, b&#7841;n n&ecirc;n c&#7853;p nh&#7853;t c&aacute;c ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh h&#7895; tr&#7907; t&#7915; Shopee ho&#7863;c l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c v&#7899;i agency.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2775\" data-end=\"2861\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2777\" data-end=\"2861\">N&#7897;i dung video n&ecirc;n <stro